<!DOCTYPE html>
<h1 id="name">Jon Grover</h1>
<h3 id="title">VP, Product Management</h3>
<div id="bio">
	<h3>VP, Product Management</h3>
	<div id="preview">
		<p>Jon Grover has eight years of experience in product development and operations.</p>
		<p>He leads the product team in designing, organizing, and managing the tools and features Mindshare's development team builds.</p>
	</div>
	<p>Jon has made major contributions from various positions at Mindshare Technologies, including multiple management roles in our products and operations departments. He works closely with clients to understand their business needs and builds products that help them improve their operations.</p>
	<p>Jon manages and oversees the Product Management Group and its activities. He operates conjointly with the development team and other cross-functional department leads to design, build, and deploy Mindshare&rsquo;s advanced customer feedback technology.</p>
	<p>Jon&rsquo;s passion for technology and improving processes has allowed him to be one of Mindshare&rsquo;s innovative leaders. As such, he spearheaded Mindshare&rsquo;s Dashboard, Mobile App, and Social Media strategy. His background and training in Scrum and Agile development processes has helped him coordinate the culture shift and process changes required for Mindshare to adopt an Agile development process. This shift has resulted in greater efficiency and transparency for Mindshare&rsquo;s development team.</p>
	<p>He believes in a persona-based strategy and that people who ignore design ignore people.</p>
	<p>Jon graduated with a B.S. in information systems from Brigham Young University. He is Product Owner, Scrum Master, and Pragmatic Marketing certified.</p>
</div>